org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.metadata

Class ResourceBundleMetaTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.metadata.MetaTag
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.metadata.ResourceBundleMetaTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMetaInfo, ISourceLocation, IMetaTag

    public class ResourceBundleMetaTag
extends MetaTag
    Represents an ResourceBundle metadata tag, of the form [ResourceBundle("bundlename")]. This is the definition version, that is created by the ResourceBundleTagNode so that we don't need the AST.
